      "description": "Solid, honest classic with plenty of charm and a great entry point into vintage motoring. This is a fair-condition driver that shows visible age, cosmetic wear, and the kind of imperfections you\u2019d expect from an older car, but it still presents as an enjoyable car you can get in and use. A good fit for someone who values character and usability over show-level perfection.",
