      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for someone who wants inexpensive transportation or a solid project to put their own touch on. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values value over perfection, but it still offers the kind of utility and potential that make budget-friendly vehicles worth a look. Priced to sell and easy to justify for the right buyer.",
