    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an inexpensive car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great chance for someone who wants affordable wheels, a project, or a practical backup vehicle. A straightforward, budget-friendly option that could really suit a handy buyer. Priced to make sense and ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong value for someone wanting an affordable driver or solid project platform. This car shows its age cosmetically, but the powertrain pulls through the rev range, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed enough for daily use. A straightforward, mechanical-spec car with good bones for the price\u2014ideal for a hands-on owner who wants dependable transportation now and room to improve over time. Priced to move and well below nicer examples, but still presenting as a capable, usable car rather than a parts-piece.",
      "price": 5950.0,
